&lt;p>htmlspecialchars — Convert special characters to HTML entities &lt;br>
Ref: &lt;a href="https://www.php.net/manual/en/function.htmlspecialchars.php" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.php.net/manual/en/function.htmlspecialchars.php&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
