&lt;h3>Deserialization with &lt;a href="https://github.com/ambionics/phpggc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">phpggc&lt;/a>&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="deserialization-with-phpggchttpsgithubcomambionicsphpggc">&lt;/span>
