&lt;p>PHPGGC is a library of unserialize() payloads along with a tool to generate them, from command line or programmatically.&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>If you need to find libraries used by the application, look for &lt;code>composer.json&lt;/code> or &lt;code>composer.lock&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
